equ <- NULL
equ <- function(x1,x2){
  gr <-1.1
  num_gen <- 30
  generation <- 1:num_gen
  N1 <- rep (0, num_gen)
  N2 <- rep (0, num_gen)
  a12 <- 0.6
  a21 <- 1.2
  K1 <- 100
  K2 <- 120
  N1[1] <- x1
  N2[1] <- x2
  for (i in 2:num_gen) {
    N1[i] = N1[i-1] + (3.2* N1[i-1] * ((K1-N1[i-1]-(a12*N2[i-1]))/K1))
    N2[i] = N2[i-1] + (gr* N2[i-1] * ((K2-N2[i-1]-(a21*N1[i-1]))/K2))
    generation[1]=1
  print (N1[i])
     if (N1[1]>0){
    plot(N1~generation,typ="b",ylim=c(0,min(c(K1,K2))),ylab="N")
  }  else {
    plot(N1~generation,typ="n",ylim=c(0,min(c(K1,K2))),ylab="N")
  }
  print(N2[i])
  if (N2[1]>0){
    lines(N2~generation,typ="b",col=3,ylim=c(0,min(c(K1,K2))),ylab="N")} else {
    plot(N2~generation,typ="n",ylim=c(0,min(c(K1,K2))),ylab="N")
  }
  }
  
}

saveGIF({
  equ(6,6)
}, interval = 0.1, movie.name = "competing_model.gif")
